Maintainer: Belay Birlie Yimer <belaybirlie.yimer@manchester.ac.uk>
Description: Prepare electronic prescription data (such as from CPRD) into an analysis-ready format, with start and stop dates for each patient's prescriptions. Based on Pye et al (2018) <https://doi.org/10.1002/pds.4440>.
